customfieldvalues.customfieldvalue:
To import 0.94 exported file in 0.96 cluster or onwards, you need to set system property &quot;hbase.import.version&quot; when running the import command as below:<br/>
<br/>
./bin/hbase -Dhbase.import.version=0.94 org.apache.hadoop.hbase.mapreduce.Import &lt;table name&gt; &lt;import file folder&gt;
